name: Chaos of Kurama
intro: Save the village from the 9 tails beast!

name: I want to be a Hokage.
intro: The all-time foot-dragger from next door keeps saying he wants to be Hokage. Let me teach him a lesson.

name: Iruka
intro: Practice with Teacher Iruka to check recent progress.

name: Sakura
intro: Sakura from Class 7, an adorable girl.

name: Sasuke
intro: Sasuke from Class 7, a cool genius. Sakura always looks at him in a strange way.

name: Kakashi
intro: Teacher of Class 7, always carrying a sleepy look.

name: Gai
intro: Master Gai wants to get involved, too.

name: Partners
intro: Have a go with little friends.

name: Challenge Class 7
intro: Let me challenge the whole of Class 7 and become a qualified Ninja.

name: 1st Quest
intro: Very first Quest, convoy grandpa to build a bridge.

name: Land of Mist
intro: A simple looking Quest, opponents seem pretty strong though.

name: Awful Consignor
intro: It‘s a very powerful opponent. Grandpa wasn‘t honest about the Quest. What an Awful Consignor.

name: Gaara
intro: Looks like another guy‘s come looking for trouble.

name: Practice 1
intro: There‘s no doubt that the enemy is going to look to make a comeback. Use the time you‘ve got to train and increase your strength.

name: Practice 2
intro: Hurry up and continue your training.

name: Practice 3
intro: Before entering a decisive battle, be sure to test out the results of your training first.

name: Guard Bridge
intro: The enemy has arrived. Go defeat them and guard the bridge.

name: Chunin Exam
intro: First Quest completed finally. The next is the Chunin exam.

name: Sunaga
intro: A slight disagreement leads to conflict with Sunaga.

name: Entrance of Death Forest
intro: Avenue of exam is at Death Forest. We encounter Otogakure at the entrance of the forest who comes to make trouble.

name: Jungle
intro: In the jungle we meet a trio from Class 10.

name: Swamp
intro: There‘s no easy fight in Death Forest.

name: Riverside
intro: We meet a group of four girls by the riverside.

name: By the Central Tower
intro: Very close to the Central Tower, we encounter another wave of tough opponents.

name: Central Tower
intro: Arrived at Central Tower finally, we face the strongest rivals ahead.

name: Perverted Sage
intro: Taking a short bath break, we come across the Pervert Sage.

name: Training 1
intro: Like old friends at once, Pervert Sage decides to guide us and train us better.

name: Training 2
intro: To get ready for the Chunin exam finals, we must check our training results.

name: Finals 1
intro: The first round at the final stage, the rival is Hyuga, a forever A-grade student with a privileged background.

name: Finals 2
intro: The competitor in the second round final is Temari from Sunagakure.

name: Finals 3
intro: The third round final is against the talented Sasuke from the same class.

name: Finals 4
intro: Gaara from Sunagakure is the last rival, mystical and tough looking.

name: Under Attack
intro: Suddenly enemies arrived. The exam has to wait.

name: Coming Otogakure
intro: Otogakures are launching a great invasion. Get ready to get on the battlefield.

name: Sasuke‘s Choice
intro: Sasuke wants to escape at this crucial moment. We must stop him.

name: Wrath
intro: Gaara is also enraged.

name: Anbu
intro: Anbus are also here. Are they friends or foes?

name: Yakushi Kabuto
intro: Among the attacking Otogakures appears Yakushi Kabuto. Surprisingly, he serves Orochimaru.

name: Orochimaru 1
intro: Finally, Orochimaru appears.

name: Orochimaru 2
intro: Get ready for the final battle against Orochimaru, protect Konoha Village at all costs.

name: Take Sasuke Back
intro: Orochimaru‘s trying to take Sasuke away. We can‘t let this happen.

name: New Enemies
intro: After the big battle, on the way in search of Tsunade to become the new Hokage, we encounter new enemies.

name: Kisame
intro: As well as Kisame, they‘re all s-rank criminals listed as wanted.

name: Duo of Kisame
intro: Kisame and his partner are very tough opponents.

name: Practice Again
intro: You‘re too weak to handle new enemies. Let Pervert Sage train you more and make you better.

name: Tanzaku Quarters
intro: We unexpectedly meet our old friends Kabuto and Orochimaru, who are also after Tsunade.

name: Legendary Fat Sheep
intro: Finally we found Tsunade, but she turned down the Hokage offer. The disagreement leads to a battle.

name: Legendary Sannin
intro: The legendary Sannin are having a tangled fight.

name: Farewell
intro: Sasuke left after all. Nothing can change his mind.

name: Another Trial
intro: Teacher Kakashi, it‘s been a good while. Please practice with us and check our progress.

name: Old Friends
intro: Of course, a friendly battle with an old friend.

name: Urgent Report
intro: An Urgent Report just arrived: Sunagakure is under attack and Gaara has been taken away by Akatsuki. Let‘s go help.

name: Under Attack 1
intro: We encounter Kisame‘s attack.

name: Under Attack 2
intro: Now it‘s Itachi‘s turn.

name: Under Attack 3
intro: The troublesome duo of Kisame again…

name: Seal
intro: After defeating the duo of Kisame, we are stopped by the Seal set by Akatsuki.

name: Art of Blast
intro: We meet a crazy artist after breaking the Seal.

name: Seal 2
intro: After the fight against the so-called artist, here‘s another Seal.

name: Red Sand
intro: The next opponent is Sasori, another psycho who claims to be an artist.

name: Final
intro: Final combat with two artists to rescue Gaara.

name: New Member
intro: Sasuke‘s place in Class 7 has been replaced by a new member, Sai. Let‘s try his strength.

name: Contact 1
intro: Dress up as Sasori to connect with Kabuto.

name: Contact 2
intro: Damn, it‘s a trap. Orochimaru‘s also here.

name: Snake Pit 1
intro: Sasuke has been training in Orochimaru‘s headquarters all these years; he‘s substantially stronger than before.

name: Snake Pit 2
intro: A tangled fight at Orochimaru‘s headquarters.

name: New Quest
intro: Rumor has it that Akatsuki has been collecting Tailed Beasts everywhere. From now on we must do everything in our power to contend with them.

name: Evil God
intro: We meet a member of Akatsuki, who enjoys self-abuse and always behaves oddly.

name: Undead
intro: It‘s another immortal opponent.

name: Undying Duo
intro: It‘s not easy to handle the Undying Duo.

name: Latest News
intro: Kabuto comes with news; Orochimaru has been killed by Sasuke.

name: Masked Man
intro: We meet a new member of Akatsuki, a mystical Masked Man.

name: Ultimate Art
intro: Big battle against Masked Man and Psycho artist.

name: Brothers
intro: The final combat against the Brothers of Uchiha Clan.

name: Taka Team 1
intro: Sasuke has founded Taka Team after taking care of Orochimaru. Now he gives us trouble, too.

name: Taka Team 2
intro: Defeat another member from Taka Team.

name: Taka Team 3
intro: Big fight against Taka Team.

name: Land of Rain
intro: The secret leader of Akatsuki is said to be hiding in the Land of Rain. Let‘s go look for some information.

name: Paper Folding
intro: Here comes another new member of Akatsuki Konan, who‘s an expert in Paper Folding.

name: Hidden Rain
intro: Ninjas from the Land of Rain are approaching.

name: Six Paths
intro: Prepare for the fight against the powerful rival Pain Six Paths.

name: Puppet Master
intro: Great combat against Pain and Konan.

name: Great Invasion
intro: Previous actions has enraged Akatsuki, who‘s carrying out a great invasion on us.

name: Protect Konoha 1
intro: Under Akatsuki‘s unceasing attacks, Konoha is in danger.

name: Protect Konoha 2
intro: We‘ll fight for Konoha until death! Let‘s finish this bunch of enemies first.

name: Protect Konoha 3
intro: Now take care of more enemies.

name: Protect Konoha 4
intro: The mystical Tobi comes as well.

name: Protect Konoha 5
intro: The number of enemies is growing increasingly. We‘ll crack soon.

name: Protect Konoha 6
intro: Yakushi Kabuto shows up in the mess.

name: Battle of the Konoha
intro: Battle with attacking Pain.

name: Ninja World War
intro: Tobi announces the start of the 4th Ninja World War.

name: Edo Tensei 1
intro: Kabuto brought many dead enemies back alive by forbidden technique.

name: Edo Tensei 2
intro: Revived enemies are becoming more and more, and they‘re all toughies.

name: Edo Tensei 3
intro: Revived enemies are becoming more and more, and they‘re all toughies. Hang on! We must hang on!

name: Puppet Master
intro: Frivolous Tobi, the Black Hand behind Akatsuki, has finally been defeated.

name: Chief Criminal
intro: Finish the Chief Criminal who made use of the forbidden technique.

name: Final
intro: Combat against Madara, for World Peace.

name: Unlimited Tsukuyomi
intro: Failed in stopping the infinite Tsukuyomi, all the strong rivals appear in illusion.

name: Pain & Itachi
intro: At the other side of the Ninja World War, you have discovered that Pain and Itachi have escaped the control of Edo Tensei

name: Kazekage
intro: The 5 Kages have been revived by Edo Tensei and have now decided to work together. KazeKage is the first to go.

name: Tsuchikage
intro: The second is Tsuchikage.

name: Raikage
intro: Then Raikage.

name: Mizukage
intro: Later Mizukage.

name: Hokage
intro: The last is Hokage.

name: Sage Kabuto
intro: Fight the person behind all this - Kabuto

name: 5 Kages
intro: Ninja World War is about to come to an end. The 5 kages are all here.

name: Ninja Alliance
intro: The justice side has organized a ninja alliance to stop Madara and Tobi.

name: Hokages
intro: All Hokages have been called up by Orochimaru for war.

name: New Sannin
intro: Sannin of Konoha are here to fight.

name: Ten Tails
intro: Tobi has become Jinchuriki by accident.

name: True Dream
intro: We need to stop Tobi for the true dream

name: The power of the people
intro: The power of the people can’t be underestimated.

name: Final
intro: Madara is reviving through Gedō - Rinne. Defeat him.

name: Betray
intro: Zetsu has betrayed Madara and absorbed his energy.

name: Final Battle
intro: The final battle has begun.

name: Eternal Nightmare
intro: We were unable to stop Infinite Tsukuyomi, the eternal nightmare has now begun.

name: Inheritor 1
intro: Inheriting the will of our fallen comrades, it‘s time for the final battle.

name: Inheritor 2
intro: To save the world, defeat the final boss.

name: Naruto and Sasuke 1
intro: Defeated the final boss, but Sasuke suddenly seals the Tailed Beasts!

name: Naruto and Sasuke 2
intro: We will need to beat Sasuke in order to undo the Infinite Tsukuyomi

name: Naruto and Sasuke 3
intro: The final battle between Naruto and Sasuke.

name: Seal of Reconciliation
intro: The friends reconcile in the end, bearing the consequences of their love and hate, and moved on.

name: Uzumaki Boruto
intro: The story of Uzumaki Boruto has begun.

name: 3-Man Team
intro: The training of the new Ino-Shika-Cho trio.

name: Old Kage‘s Gathering
intro: The previous 5 Kages gather, reminiscing about their pasts and also training their predecessors at the same time.
